NK041(di)033:1: // bla bslu 'chi bdag gi g.yul las rgyal ba slob dpon chen pos gnang ba bzhugs so //
NK041(di)033:3: bla bslu'i glud 'di sngon gyi dus na slob dpon
NK041(di)033:4: pad+mas bod kyi lha 'dre thams cad dam la btags
NK041(di)033:5: nas rgyal khams bde la bkod pa'i dus su gdug
NK041(di)033:6: pa can gyi lha srin gcig lus pa des 'gro
NK041(di)033:7: ba yongs kyi tshe srog la rgol ba gcig byung
NK041(di)033:8: ste / rgyal bu mu khyud 'dzin zhes bya ba
NK041(di)033:9: nad kyis thebs nas ci byas kyang ma phan te
NK041(di)033:10: ste / / de'i dus lha 'dre des bla khyer 'dug pa la /
NK041(di)033:11: rgyal blon thams cad bka' bgros mdzad nas slob dpon pad+ma la zhus pas /
NK041(di)033:12: slob dpon gyi zhal nas kho lha srin thams cad
NK041(di)033:13: kyi nang nas gdug pa che ba lus 'dug pa
NK041(di)033:14: / da de la bla bslu byed dgos pas kho rang bsod nams kyi shan 'byed dgos pa 'dug /
NK041(di)033:15: shwa phyi la lha la shwa dkar po 'bul /
NK041(di)033:17: lha shwa che na bslu bar rigs /
NK041(di)033:18: 'dre shwa che na bslu bar mi rigs gsungs pas /
NK041(di)033:19: rgyal bas shwa brgyab pas lha shwa che bar byung bas da bla bslu ba yin gsungs nas /
NK041(di)033:21: de la bla gang yin gyi gzugs dang /
NK041(di)033:33: mkhan pa ste li sder ram /
NK041(di)033:34: bal sder gang rigs kyi nang du bla rdzas de
NK041(di)033:35: rnams bcug la phor pas kha bcad la nas bre
NK041(di)033:37: lha glud dkar po la lha shwa dkar po phul la bzhag /
NK041(di)033:38: 'dre glud nag po la 'dre shwa nag po mdun du gtad la bzhag go //
NK041(di)033:39: mda' rgod sgro ma gcig la dar dkar po kha gang btags pa dang /
NK041(di)033:40: nad pa la dril ba'i glud gcig gi mthar zhwa gos lhwam gsum bzhag /
NK041(di)033:41: tshe thar phrog tshang ba zhig kyang bzhag nas smreng gis bsngo ba ni 'di skad do //
NK041(di)033:43: sangs rgyas rkang gnyis gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)033:44: chos nyid chags dang bral te bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)033:45: dge 'dun 'dus pa'i gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)033:46: bden pa'i mchog ni dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' //
NK041(di)033:47: dkon mchog bka' la mi nyan gang yang med //
NK041(di)033:48: ri rab zom la mi gnas gang yang med //
NK041(di)033:49: rgya mtsho'i chu la mi 'thung gang yang med //
NK041(di)033:50: 'byung ba lnga la mi brten gang yang med //
NK041(di)033:51: nyi zla'i 'od kyis mi khyab gang yang med //
NK041(di)033:52: mtho ba srid pa'i rtse mo man chad nas //
NK041(di)033:53: dma' ba na rag dmyal khams yan chad du //
NK041(di)033:54: 'phags pa'i spyan gyis gzigs pa'i sa //
NK041(di)033:55: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre kun //
NK041(di)033:56: sngags 'chang bdag gi ngag la nyon //
NK041(di)033:57: dang po bla bslu gang du srid //
NK041(di)033:58: slob dpon pad+ma'i thugs rje yis //
NK041(di)033:59: mu khyud 'dzin pa bdud las bslus //
NK041(di)033:60: bar du bla bslu gang du dar //
NK041(di)033:61: yi dam lha yi thugs rje yis //
NK041(di)033:62: srog chags thams cad tshe bsring mdzad //
NK041(di)033:63: tha ma bla bslu gang du byed //
NK041(di)033:67: dus dang bskal pa de tsam la //
NK041(di)033:68: skyob par byed pa'i lha gcig srid //
NK041(di)033:69: gnod par byed pa'i 'dre gcig srid //
NK041(di)033:71: lha la lha shwa dkar po 'bul //
NK041(di)033:72: lha shwa dkar po lha yis btab //
NK041(di)033:73: lha shwa de ni che bar byung //
NK041(di)033:75: 'dre shwa de ni chung bar byung //
NK041(di)033:76: shwa de che ba lha yis thob //
NK041(di)033:77: chung ba de ni 'dre yis thob //
NK041(di)033:78: lha yang rgyal la 'dre yang pham //
NK041(di)033:81: bla yi lu gu dkar po la //
NK041(di)033:82: ya mtshan can gyi dar snas brgyan //
NK041(di)033:83: bla yi rten du khyod bstsal lo //
NK041(di)033:84: bla rkang g.yas pa bla yi rten //
NK041(di)033:85: bla rkang 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:86: dung shwa dkar po bla yi shwa /
NK041(di)033:87: dung shwa 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:88: bla g.yu gru dkar bla yi bkrag /
NK041(di)033:89: bla g.yu 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:90: 'chang lang smug po bla yi rten //
NK041(di)033:92: bye ru dmar po bla yi khrag /
NK041(di)033:93: bye ru 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:94: bla rdo dkar po bla yi rdo //
NK041(di)033:95: bla rdo 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:96: bla shing shug pa bla yi shing //
NK041(di)033:97: bla shing 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:98: mkhan bu r+ts+wa bzang bla yi zas //
NK041(di)033:99: mkhan bu 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:100: bla mtsho sngon mo bla yi mtsho //
NK041(di)033:101: bla mtsho 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:102: nas dkar bre gang lha la 'bul //
NK041(di)033:103: nas dkar 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:104: dar tshon sna lnga bla yi bkrag /
NK041(di)033:105: dar tshon 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:106: tshon skud sna lnga bla yi lding //
NK041(di)033:107: bla lding 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)033:108: gshin gyi bla glud ma yin gyi //
NK041(di)033:109: gson gyi bla glud 'di longs la //
NK041(di)033:110: bla bzung thongs la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)033:111: bsdams pa lhod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)033:113: bslu yang gcig la bslu yang gnyis //
NK041(di)033:114: gsum gyi bar du bslu bar bya //
NK041(di)033:124: bla yi lu gu la gsol lo //
NK041(di)033:127: khyod 'go ba'i lha la zhal yar ltos //
NK041(di)033:128: srung ma'i lha la zhal yar ltos //
NK041(di)033:129: skyob pa'i lha la zhal yar ltos //
NK041(di)033:130: le'u'i lha la zhal yar ltos //
NK041(di)033:132: dang po su dang su yi bla //
NK041(di)033:134: rgyal bu mu khyud 'dzin pa dang //
NK041(di)033:135: lag na rdo rje'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK041(di)033:136: dge slong kun dga' bo yi bla //
NK041(di)033:137: snang srid sde brgyad lag nas bslus //
NK041(di)033:138: da lta su dang su yi bla //
NK041(di)033:139: da ltar rdo rje 'dzin pa ngas //
NK041(di)033:140: snang srid sde brgyad lag pa nas //
NK041(di)033:141: sbyin bdag 'di yi bla yang bslu //
NK041(di)033:142: ya bdud rgyal po la sogs te //
NK041(di)033:143: bdud kyi sde tshogs bsam mi khyab //
NK041(di)033:144: khyod rnams lag na bla yod srid //
NK041(di)033:145: khyod rnams lag na bla yod na //
NK041(di)033:146: gshin gyi bla glud ma yin gyi //
NK041(di)033:147: gson gyi bla glud 'di longs la //
NK041(di)033:148: bla bzung thongs la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)033:149: bsdams pa klod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)033:150: lan chags bu lon byang bar gyis //

NK041(di)033:154: khyod rnams lag na bla yod na //

NK041(di)033:158: bsdams pa klod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)033:159: lan chags bu lon byang bar gyis //

NK041(di)033:161: gnod sbyin sde tshogs bsam mi khyab //

NK041(di)033:164: bla glud bla bzung thongs la bsdams pa klod la
NK041(di)033:165: lan chags bu lon gtsug na rin chen la sogs
NK041(di)033:166: te // klu yi sde tshogs khyod rnams khyod rnams
NK041(di)033:167: gshin gyi gson gyi bla bzung bsdams pa lan chags
